### DIAGNOSIS: Mengapa Momentum Exit SELALU Rugi?

#### Mekanisme Kegagalan (Step by Step)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Bot entry LONG\n(momentum masih OK)"] --> B["Market mulai turun\n(-0.5% sampai -1.5%)"]
    B --> C{"Layer 5: 15m trend\nmasih uptrend?"}
    C -->|"Ya (EMA20>EMA50)"| D["Override threshold → 2%\n⚠️ MENUNGGU sampai -2%"]
    C -->|Tidak| E["Pakai dynamic threshold\n~0.5-1.2% (ATR-based)"]
    D --> F["Harga terus turun...\n-1.5%... -1.8%... -2.0%"]
    F --> G["Akhirnya trigger di -2.0%\n= ROE -50% 💀"]
    E --> H["Trigger lebih awal\n= kerugian lebih kecil"]
    
    style D fill:#ff4444,color:white
    style G fill:#ff0000,color:white
    style H fill:#44aa44,color:white
```

#### 5 Masalah Arsitektural

| # | Masalah | Dampak | Severity |
|---|---------|--------|----------|
| 1 | **HTF override menghapus dynamic threshold** | Momentum exit jadi fixed 2% stop-loss | 🔴 CRITICAL |
| 2 | **Threshold 2% × 25x leverage = -50% ROE** | Setiap trigger = setengah modal posisi hilang | 🔴 CRITICAL |
| 3 | **Tidak ada max concurrent position limit** saat exit | 5+ posisi LONG kena dump bersamaan | 🔴 CRITICAL |
| 4 | **EMA/RSI/MACD pasti sudah bearish** di -2% | Layer 3-4 jadi rubber stamp, bukan filter | 🟡 HIGH |
| 5 | **Indikator dihitung dari 1m candle close** | Lag 1 menit minimum, di crypto = fatal | 🟡 HIGH |

#### Bukti: Apa yang Terjadi pada 3 Trade Terburuk

**BLUR (-$5.78, adverse -2.18%)**
- Entry: $0.028023 → Exit: $0.027413
- Score 55 (low confidence, seharusnya TIDAK di-entry)
- Notional $266 × 25x leverage = modal kecil tapi kerugian besar
- 15m EMA masih uptrend → threshold di-override ke 2%
- Pada saat trigger, harga sudah turun 2.18% = **terlambat ~1.7% dari threshold normal**

**TIA (-$5.63, adverse -2.12%)**
- Entry: $0.454975 → Exit: $0.445344
- Score 54 (minimum entry threshold!)
- Pattern identik: HTF override → tunggu sampai -2% → exit terlambat

**BERA (-$5.45, adverse -2.22%)**
- Entry: $0.416238 → Exit: $0.406990
- Adverse move TERTINGGI (2.22%), notional $245
- Kalau pakai threshold normal (ATR-based ~0.5-1%), exit di ~-0.8% → kerugian cuma ~-$2.00

