## DELIVERABLE: REKOMENDASI PHASE 2

### 1. Momentum Exit → **MATIKAN, GANTI ARSITEKTUR**

**Aksi Segera:**
```python
# config.py line 264
momentum_exit_enabled: bool = False  # ← MATIKAN SEGERA
```

**Arsitektur Pengganti — "Smart Trail" (Proposal):**

Alih-alih menunggu kerugian besar lalu exit, gunakan:

| Mekanisme | Trigger | Aksi |
|-----------|---------|------|
| **Early Trail** (sudah ada) | Profit ≥ 0.5% lalu retrace 0.3% | ✅ Sudah bekerja baik |
| **Break-Even Stop** (baru) | Setelah 10 menit + pernah profit ≥ 0.3% | Pindahkan SL ke entry + fee |
| **Time-Decay Exit** (baru) | Setiap 5 menit tanpa profit baru → kurangi threshold | Progressive exit |
| **Hard SL** (sudah ada) | Loss ≥ 3% | ✅ Backstop, jarang kena |

### 2. Signal Score → **REBUILD TOTAL**

**Target: Correlation > 0.3 dengan PnL**

**Roadmap Rebuild:**

| Step | Aksi | Detail |
|------|------|--------|
| 1 | **Hapus redundansi** | Pilih SATU dari: EMA cross / Momentum candles / HH-HL structure |
| 2 | **Rebalance bobot** | Fundamental (OI/Funding) = 40%, Teknikal = 30%, Microstructure (OB/CVD) = 30% |
| 3 | **Tambah regime filter** | Score × regime_multiplier (trending=1.2, ranging=0.7, volatile=0.5) |
| 4 | **Naikkan minimum threshold** | min_score → 62 (dari 57). Data: score 60-64 WR=80% |
| 5 | **Tambah mean-reversion guard** | Jika RSI>60 + price >EMA21 → CAP score di 60 (jangan entry di puncak) |
| 6 | **Time-decay scoring** | Score berkurang seiring waktu sejak signal dibuat (stale signal = bad signal) |

### 3. Risk Management → **TAMBAH PORTFOLIO-LEVEL GUARD**

| Guard | Parameter | Efek |
|-------|-----------|------|
| **Max correlated positions** | Max 2 posisi LONG bersamaan | Cegah 8 posisi kena dump bareng |
| **Sector exposure cap** | Max $300 notional per "arah" | Limit total kerugian satu arah |
| **Momentum exit cooldown** | Jika 1 momentum exit terjadi → BLOK entry baru 30 menit | Cegah masuk ke market yang sedang dump |
| **Dynamic position sizing** | Score 55-59 → 50% size, Score 60+ → 100% size | Kurangi risiko di sinyal lemah |

